<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {{
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }}

        .email-container {{
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }}

        .header {{
            background-color: #f44336;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }}

        .header h1 {{
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }}

        .content {{
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }}

        .content h2 {{
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #f44336;
        }}

        .content p {{
            margin: 10px 0;
        }}

        .content a {{
            color: #f44336;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }}

        .content a:hover {{
            text-decoration: underline;
        }}

        .error-button {{
            background-color: #f44336;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none !important;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }}

        .error-button:hover {{
            background-color: #da190b;
        }}

        .footer {{
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }}

        .footer a {{
            color: #f44336;
            text-decoration: none;
        }}

        .emoji {{
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }}

        .error-box {{
            background-color: #ffebee;
            border-left: 4px solid #f44336;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }}

        @media (max-width: 600px) {{
            .content h2 {{
                font-size: 18px;
            }}

            .header h1 {{
                font-size: 20px;
            }}

            .error-button {{
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }}
        }}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1><span class="emoji">‚õîÔ∏è</span> Build Error <span class="emoji">‚õîÔ∏è</span></h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Build Failed</h2>

            <p>Unfortunately, there was an issue with your build process.</p>

            <div class="error-box">
                <p><strong>Error Details:</strong></p>
                <p>{error_message}</p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{build_logs_url}" class="error-button">
                    <span class="emoji">üîç</span> View Build Logs
                </a>
            </div>

            <p>Please review the build logs to identify and resolve the issue. If you need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out for support.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>